<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Touchpoint Analysis — Cyrus Garcia</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --serif: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;

    --ink: #1a1a18;
    --muted: #6b6b66;
    --rule: #e0dfd8;
    --surface: #f5f4f0;
    --white: #ffffff;

    --blue-bg: #E6F1FB;
    --blue-bd: #85B7EB;
    --blue-tx: #0C447C;
    --green-bg: #E1F5EE;
    --green-bd: #5DCAA5;
    --green-tx: #085041;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  body {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3.5rem 3rem 4rem;
  }

  /* Eyebrow */
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* H1 */
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  /* Subtitle */
  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  /* HR */
  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Meta row */
  .meta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* Section */
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
  }

  .section-body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .section-body p + p {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Chart container */
  .chart-block {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .chart-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .chart-panel {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
  }

  .chart-panel-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .chart-canvas-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 180px;
  }

  /* Portfolio avg panel */
  .portfolio-rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .portfolio-row-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .bar-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .bar-track {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 8px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .bar-fill.before {
    width: 100%;
    background: #B5D4F4;
  }

  .bar-fill.after {
    width: 74%;
    background: var(--blue-tx);
  }

  .bar-value {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    min-width: 28px;
  }

  .portfolio-summary {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }

  .portfolio-summary-number {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .portfolio-summary-desc {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  .chart-footnote {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
  }

  /* Metrics row */
  .metrics-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .metric-tile {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .metric-desc {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    padding-top: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer-left {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-right {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .footer-right a {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .footer-right a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Eyebrow + H1 + Subtitle -->
  <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio Case Study — 2025</p>
  <h1>How a Touchpoint Analysis Informed a Strategic Pivot</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">A reconstruction of an operational analysis that contributed to Green Think Energy's acquisition by Enphase Energy.</p>

  <hr>

  <!-- Meta Row -->
  <div class="meta-row">
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Role</span>
      <span class="meta-value">COO</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Scope</span>
      <span class="meta-value">Production Operations, 13+ person team</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Outcome</span>
      <span class="meta-value">Strategic capacity reallocation</span>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- The Problem -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">The Problem</p>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p>Revenue was climbing alongside a growing client base, but operational load was not tracking with project volume in an expected way. During a seasonally slow winter month, revision volume was high, but it was not coming from enterprise accounts. I traced those revisions to smaller clients and recognized the pattern warranted a closer look at service cost by account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- The Approach -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">The Approach</p>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p>Using Salesforce project management data joined with financial records, I constructed a per-client view of total operational effort, summing all project versions, pooling them by client, and dividing by annual project count. This mapped the full-service cost of each account and allowed touchpoints to be plotted against client volume tier.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- The Finding -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">The Finding</p>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p>After defining client volume breakpoints, I found that small clients required approximately 4.0 touches per project compared to roughly 1.3 for enterprise accounts. The long-tail customer base was consuming a disproportionate share of production operations capacity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Chart -->
  <div class="chart-block">
    <div class="chart-grid">
      <div class="chart-panel">
        <p class="chart-panel-label">Avg. touches per project by client tier</p>
        <div class="chart-canvas-wrap">
          <canvas id="tierChart" role="img" aria-label="Bar chart: low-volume clients average 4.0 touches per project, mid-volume 1.7, high-volume 1.3."></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-panel">
        <p class="chart-panel-label">Portfolio avg. touches</p>
        <div class="portfolio-rows">
          <div>
            <p class="portfolio-row-label">Before</p>
            <div class="bar-row">
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill before"></div></div>
              <span class="bar-value">1.84</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="portfolio-row-label">After</p>
            <div class="bar-row">
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill after"></div></div>
              <span class="bar-value">1.37</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="portfolio-summary">
            <p class="portfolio-summary-number">26%</p>
            <p class="portfolio-summary-desc">reduction across portfolio</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="chart-footnote">Illustrative representation. Proprietary data not disclosed; figures are directional.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- The Decision -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">The Decision</p>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p>The data arrived at a real crossroads: we could hire more plan set designers or more software developers, but not both. I presented the findings to the CEO/CTO in February and recommended deprioritizing long-tail clients to free capacity for software development. Rather than cutting small clients, we restructured pricing. Clients could commit to higher volume for a discounted monthly rate, or shift to per-project prepayment at retail. The change was implemented in March, ahead of the spring surge.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- The Outcome -->
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">The Outcome</p>
    <div class="metrics-row">
      <div class="metric-tile">
        <p class="metric-value">~5%</p>
        <p class="metric-desc">revenue decrease</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-tile">
        <p class="metric-value">~25%</p>
        <p class="metric-desc">operational capacity freed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-tile">
        <p class="metric-value">1.84→1.37</p>
        <p class="metric-desc">portfolio-wide touches per project</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p>Clients who could not prepay and generated outsized rework fell out naturally. Larger entities moved to upfront payment, freeing working capital. The recovered capacity funded accelerated software development, technology that ultimately became the foundation for Enphase's Solargraf permitting platform, reducing permit plan creation time by up to 95%. The segment we deprioritized is now served by software at scale.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <span class="footer-left">Cyrus Garcia · Operations &amp; Systems</span>
    <span class="footer-right"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cyrus-garcia-631054138" target="_blank" rel="noopener">linkedin.com/in/cyrus-garcia-631054138</a></span>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  new Chart(document.getElementById('tierChart'), {
    type: 'bar',
    data: {
      labels: ['Low-volume', 'Mid-volume', 'High-volume'],
      datasets: [{
        data: [4.0, 1.7, 1.3],
        backgroundColor: ['#B5D4F4', '#378ADD', '#0C447C'],
        borderWidth: 0,
        borderRadius: 4
      }]
    },
    options: {
      responsive: true,
      maintainAspectRatio: false,
      plugins: {
        legend: { display: false },
        tooltip: {
          callbacks: {
            label: (ctx) => ' ' + ctx.parsed.y.toFixed(1) + ' touches per project'
          }
        }
      },
      scales: {
        x: {
          grid: { display: false },
          ticks: {
            font: { family: "'DM Mono', monospace", size: 10 },
            color: '#6b6b66'
          }
        },
        y: {
          beginAtZero: true,
          max: 5,
          grid: { color: 'rgba(107,107,102,0.12)' },
          ticks: {
            stepSize: 1,
            font: { family: "'DM Mono', monospace", size: 10 },
            color: '#6b6b66',
            callback: (v) => v.toFixed(1)
          }
        }
      }
    }
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
